repository.name: ticketing
repository.description: The microservice-based web application allows users to list tickets for events, purchase tickets, and manage orders and payments. The application is built using Typescript, Next.js, React, Docker, Redis, NATS, and JavaScript. The application has been successfully deployed on Digital Ocean.
